text: Vasco Ramires Jr. (born 28 September 1964) is a Portuguese equestrian. He competed in two events at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1964 births Category:Living people Category:Portuguese male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Portugal Category:Equestrians at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Lisbon
